{"type": "article", "id": 21854, "title": "想穿西服又不想太正经，这里有5个品牌供你参考", "description": "运动鞋、靴子什么的搭在一起也挺好看的。\r\n", "date": "2016-02-05T10:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 23119, "name": "西服"}, {"id": 23129, "name": "Eidos Napoli"}, {"id": 23130, "name": "ENGINEERED GARMENTS"}, {"id": 23131, "name": "OUR LEGAC"}, {"id": 23132, "name": "THE GIGI"}, {"id": 23133, "name": "AMI"}], "category": 19, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 642, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115315B2vytUScksGKWwri.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">西服是一种古老的存在，自它问世以来，设计和制作工艺改变并不大。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">但现在没有多少人会愿意成天穿着很正式的西服去上班。一些老旧的西装品牌和新锐的设计师合作推出了一些有趣的西装设计。总的来说，这些西服设计都提倡简单随性的打扮，平易近人的气质，可以和球鞋、短靴这些单品混搭起来。</p>\n<p class=\"\">这里有几位设计师值得关注一下：</p>\n<h2>1. Eidos Napoli</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115259xLT0Z9kaiJYUs1Wb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66632653\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115300asjYLK0kbW4gnmC9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115301ukUhEt7TwD68ioN0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95142379\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115301WBxhbopLIT53EniK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94621849\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115302GAVkqypfdCELWeY7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Eidos Napoli 是来自意大利那不勒斯的男装品牌。最开始是作为另一个男装品牌的 Isaia 的兄弟品牌出现。Isaia 的明目张胆的意大利风格，Eidos Napoli 愿意提供的日常装，而且瞄准的是年轻人。“我年轻时候喜欢玩滑板，而现在休闲装正当红，老一辈的西服不太适应现在的生活方式。”<a href=\"http://www.gq.com/story/italian-style-eidos-napoli-spring-summer-2016\">设计师 Antonio Ciongoli 说。</a> Eidos Napoli 的价格大约在 1600 美元左右。</p>\n<h2>2.ENGINEERED GARMENTS</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115302kY6MxgjOsyZe2mPH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66632653\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115303gJX7YrzPkLs2mQTt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115303E5bD8njNTgGtiRZz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115304UZWhxoJ70nTu8V9X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">由设计师 Daiki Suzuki 主导的纽约时尚品牌 Engineered Garments ，对于工装文化一直情有独钟，所以你可以看到工装设计和西服的融合，完全丢掉了西服硬挺的感觉，皱巴巴的不羁感特别重。这样的西服显得格外有趣，好像是从爷爷的爷爷那里祖传而来。此外，用来做西服的布料花纹也很跳跃，不走高级灰或者高级黑路线。<br></p>\n<h2>3.OUR LEGAC</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115304Lwi7R59gf0Au3yxb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66632653\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115305UHhPbfdB1VgOIw0t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115307DueVIAwd23pStGcr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115307f7FcQ6jaNX3xu8HB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">来自瑞典的 Our Legacy 的设计带有北欧独有的极简感。这个品牌成立于 2005 年，已经有一段时间。西服有一种北欧人那种随性又木讷的风格，此外也做衬衫、夹克，格外街头和青春。</p>\n<h2>4.THE GIGI</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115308xAiKIXmO9eD8yp4P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115308YGgfLZD2dsnK1vUi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115309qPzwhKnj0ka3FEAJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115309CpAWb5Tjz37srBYf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115310Vjlu8vQiSmPKCWx2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115310vmVRJ91Mozy0nYsu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115311gje6wqpQF5Uybm8E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">又是一个来自意大利的品牌。2012年Mario and Pierluigi (Gigi)从家族企业中脱离出来做了这个品爱，slogan 也很有意思——Don't look back ，足以显示它有多不守旧。设计师擅长用羊毛材质的条纹、编制面料来做西服。</p>\n<h2>5.AMI</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115311uJUbpF1WzY0SZ49v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66632653\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115312EKmeoCuI5Q2sB3tO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50198413\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115312RQNLET02aGsnrv4i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115313IsmRoW8CJprv19a5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115314vd2jc5Z4KtMboWJg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115314lqX9m6sW0eODLvhV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">设计师 Alexandre Mattiussi 在2011 年成立 AMI 之前，在Dior, Marc Jacobs 和 Givenchy 工作过。现在这个品牌不仅设计男装也涉足了女装。设计师本人认为太正儿八经的西服对普通人来说没什么用，他做 AMI 这个品牌就是希望一般人能穿上他的设计，所以西服的设计传达出来一种轻松日常的理念。AMI 的西服有一种信手拈来的法式优雅，靴子和运动鞋搭配起来都很好看。</p>\n<p class=\"\">题图和文内图来自：Eidos Napoli @ instagram 、topgrain.co.uk、donbleek.com、i7.wimg.jp、41.media.tumblr.com、selectism.com、letsrestycle.com。</p>\n\n"}